<document>
    <header>
        <title>Heivehit davvisámi boallobeavddi ja davvisámegiela čállingiellan
        Windows 10:s</title>
    </header>
    <body>

        <p>
            Mii čájehit mo merošta davvisámegiela čállingiellan. Go vállje
            davvisámegiela čállingiellan, de čállindárkkisteaddji automáhtalaččat
            molso davvisámegillii go leat sajáiduhttán Divvun-reaidduid.
        </p>

        <ol>
            <li>Mana <strong>Start</strong>-fállui ja coahkkal
                <strong>Innstillinger</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/start_menu-no.png" alt="Startmeny"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Mana <strong>Klokkeslett og språk</strong>-merkošii:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-no.png" alt="Kontrollpanel"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Coahkkal <strong>Legg til et språk</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-time_and_lang-no.png" alt="Giella" /></p>
            </li>
            <li>Coahkkal <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-no.png" alt="Lasit giela"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Vállje dan <strong>Davvisámegieleavttu</strong> mii heive dutnje:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-norway-no.png" alt="Báikkálaš molssaeavttut"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Merke <strong>Davvisámegiella</strong> ja coahkkal <strong>Alternativer</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-modify-sme-no.png" alt="Giella maŋŋágo lea válljen davvisámegiela"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Coahkkal <strong>Legg til tastatur</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-keyboard-no.png" alt="Giellamolssaeavttut"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Vállje <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-add-sme-extended-norway-no.png" alt="Čállingiellavuohki"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Merke <strong>Norsk med samisk</strong> ja coahkkal <strong>Fjern</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/prefs-remove-norw_with_sami-keyboard-no.png"
                alt="Giellamolssaeavttut: Váldde eret «norsk med samisk»"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Dál dus lea <strong>Davvisámegiella (Norga)</strong> čállingiellan ja boallobeavdi mii gullá dasa lea <strong>Samisk, utvidet Norge</strong>:
                <p><img src="images/win10/keyboard-done-sme-no.png"
                alt="Giella go davvisámegiella lea heivehuvvon"/></p>
            </li>
            <li>Boallobeavddis deaddilat
                <strong>Windows+gaska</strong> dassáigo davvisámi boallobeavdi lea aktiiva:
                <p><img src="images/win10/switching-keyboards-sme-no.png"
                alt="Giella go davvisámegiella lea heivehuvvon"/></p>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </body>
</document>
